## **Why use our MIDI editor**
Song Maker can generate MIDI files based on your song description. Our MIDI editor allows you to listen to your creation while making further adjustments seamlessly. It also features an ABC Note editor and Audio (mp3, wav) to Midi convertor function.

## **Mac and iOS Users**  
You can use the Midify app directly from the App Store to load and play MIDI files: [Midify - Midi editor](https://apps.apple.com/app/midify/id6670599599).

## **Android Users**  
Link to download android app: [play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ailmind.midify](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ailmind.midify).

## **Windows Users**  
You can access the Midify App directly from the Microsoft Store: [Midify - Midi editor](https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9nxsw4372n3k).

If you enjoyed using Song Maker and would like to support me in improving it, please consider sponsoring here: [Support Song Maker Development](https://github.com/sponsors/sherwyn33).

## **Need Help with Song Maker?**  
For additional instructions or help with using Song Maker, please request the Instruction Manual, FAQ, available commands from the document catalog.
